Author: showmeurguacamole
Text: Thank you! Human me knows this even when my hell brain tries to say otherwise!

Author: squishykiss
Text: Your eating disorder is 100% valid and it seems like you really need some support/professional help. The “Thin enough” mindset  prevents you from ever feeling like you deserve to get help. You deserve to be happy and to live a fulfilling life that doesn’t revolve around disordered eating issues.
